            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-font-bold Step 1: Create A Ballot
            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width Go to your dashboard, click the add button in your ballots list, enter a ballot name, and click the submit button. It's as easy as that.
            br
            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-font-bold Step 2: Fill Out Your Ballot
            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width Click on a Ballot Name from the dashboard to go to the detailed view. 
            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width Click "Edit Picks" at the bottom of the page. When in edit mode, use the drop down lists to pick your teams. 
            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width Click "Save All Changes" to submit your picks. (You can change your picks for each round up until that round's first game starts).
            p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width A team is ineligible for selection if you have selected them in a previous round or if they have been eliminated from the tournament.
