        p.ms-font-size-30.ms-font-bold Creating And Joining Leagues
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-font-bold Step 1: Create a New League
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width To create a league, choose Start A League in the left nav.
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-font-bold Step 2: Add Your Ballot
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width On the League Page, click the "Add your ballot to this league" button, choose which ballot you want to add to the league, and click the + button.
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-font-bold Step 3: Invite Other Players
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width If you are the league owner, the league page will display an ID number. Invite other players by sending them the ID number and your league password.
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-font-bold Step 4: Join Other Leagues
        p.ms-font-size-20.ms-text-width After a league owner sends you their league ID and password, choose Join a League in the left nav bar, enter the id and password, and click "Join".  Add a ballot to the league by following the instructions in Step 2.
